{
  "text": "Antibiotics are one of the most commonly used classes of pharmaceuticals and are commonly detected in marine environments [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . China's shelf seas have been previously reported to be impacted by antibiotics [CITATION_3] . In this study, 23 out of the 59 screened antibiotics were detected at the 19 sampling stations.",
